{
  "id": "6586f0197dfe0c00235b28a8",
  "title": "知識のない人に合わせたコミュニケーションは参加者の多様性が高くなるほど貧しくなる",
  "created": 1703342105,
  "updated": 1703781674,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6586f0197dfe0c00235b28a8",
      "text": "知識のない人に合わせたコミュニケーションは参加者の多様性が高くなるほど貧しくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342105
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf54",
      "text": "from [2023/12/23]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342105
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f0ccaff09e0000d5c330",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342284,
      "updated": 1703342649
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf55",
      "text": "　[知識のない人に合わせたコミュニケーション]は参加者の多様性が高くなるほど貧しくなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342284
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf57",
      "text": "　　[https://gyazo.com/04cf5e82bd0b22bbc362a0a8c894cfeb]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342105
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf58",
      "text": "　　文脈: [スルーが許されるコミュニティ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342105
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf59",
      "text": "　　[スルーが許されないコミュニティ]では同質性を高めた方がコミュニケーションの質が高くなる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342105
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f0cfaff09e0000d5c331",
      "text": "\tT: ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342287,
      "updated": 1703342726
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f286aff09e0000f60fdc",
      "text": "  「知識のない人は知識ない人同士でコミュニケーションしてね」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342726,
      "updated": 1703342751
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f28faff09e0000f60fe9",
      "text": "  とか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342736,
      "updated": 1703342751
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f286aff09e0000f60fdf",
      "text": "  「知識ない人は多様性の高い場でのコミュニケーションを諦めてね」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342726,
      "updated": 1703342751
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f286aff09e0000f60fe1",
      "text": "  と言う結論はなんか嫌だなーと思う一方",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342726,
      "updated": 1703342751
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f286aff09e0000f60fe3",
      "text": "  「諦めないと無理じゃね？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342726,
      "updated": 1703342751
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f286aff09e0000f60fe5",
      "text": "  とも感じます。なんなんでしょうねー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342726,
      "updated": 1703342751
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f286aff09e0000f60fe8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342726,
      "updated": 1703342726
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f283aff09e0000f60fd9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342723,
      "updated": 1703342723
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f283aff09e0000f60fda",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342723,
      "updated": 1703342723
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f0cfaff09e0000d5c332",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342287,
      "updated": 1703342287
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf5a",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/0796de2712a9b29296e7648770954876]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342296
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf5b",
      "text": "　Aさんにとっての「価値のある会話」は、すでに知ってるXでもなく、理解が困難なBの専門性の頂点のZでもなく、自分の[知識境界]のすぐ外のYである",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342296
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf5c",
      "text": "　　[グルーミング]目的の会話を除く。その場合はXになる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342296
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f0dfaff09e0000d5c333",
      "text": "\tT:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342304,
      "updated": 1703342784
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f2bfaff09e0000b4bf6a",
      "text": "\t\tスルーを許すことでコミュニティの多様性を確保しながら質の高いコミュニケーションをすることができると。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342784,
      "updated": 1703342784
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f2baaff09e0000b4bf65",
      "text": "\t\t話題ごとにコミュニティの一部の人間のみが質の高いコミュニケーションをする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342779,
      "updated": 1703342789
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f301aff09e0000b4bf71",
      "text": "\tN:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342849,
      "updated": 1703342852
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f304aff09e0000b4bf72",
      "text": "\t\t一部の人が質の高いコミュニケーションをして、それによって生み出されるコンテンツを周囲の人がテレビのように受動的に摂取する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342853,
      "updated": 1703342853
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f2c4aff09e0000b4bf6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342789,
      "updated": 1703342789
    },
    {
      "id": "65879558aff09e00000d8e69",
      "text": "関連メモ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703384409,
      "updated": 1703384415
    },
    {
      "id": "6587955faff09e00000d8e6b",
      "text": "　「価値のある会話」の「価値」は主観的",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703384415,
      "updated": 1703384425
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f0e0aff09e0000d5c335",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342304,
      "updated": 1703342304
    },
    {
      "id": "6587f19daff09e000084483d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703408030,
      "updated": 1703408030
    },
    {
      "id": "6587f19daff09e000084483e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703408030,
      "updated": 1703408030
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf5d",
      "text": "ひとこぶの絵を描くのは「描きやすい絵のバイアス」で「一人の人が多様な同質性の高いコミュニティに所属する」が可能になるためにはそれぞれの人が多峰である必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342304
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f2dcaff09e0000b4bf6c",
      "text": "\tT:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342813,
      "updated": 1703342814
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f2dfaff09e0000b4bf6d",
      "text": "\t\t「[描きやすい絵のバイアス]」面白いですね。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342815,
      "updated": 1703342829
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f2dfaff09e0000b4bf6e",
      "text": "  それは「[考えやすいものに引っ張られる]」であって、たとえば「[誤った二分法]」もその仲間ですね",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342815,
      "updated": 1703342826
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf5e",
      "text": "　[https://gyazo.com/b7bfc7bb065114e5fea017c2a9864c32]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342305
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f0ecaff09e0000d5c336",
      "text": "　[https://gyazo.com/61983700d185d8ce2a71dddc7c0c8fde]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342316,
      "updated": 1703342316
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf60",
      "text": "　　AとBは高度なトピックXを共有して会話することができる、Bは自分の専門から高度なYを取り出してXと関連づけることができる、AはY単体では理解できないが、Xと関連づけられることで理解可能になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342296
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf61",
      "text": "　　理解可能でない場合でも口頭の会話であれば質問をすることでXとYの間のリンクを詳細化することができる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342296
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f317aff09e0000b4bf73",
      "text": "　　\tT: 口頭の必要がありますか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342872,
      "updated": 1703342873
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f319aff09e0000b4bf74",
      "text": "　\t\t\t話を忘れない程度の短い時間でやり取りするならチャットでもいいと思う[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342873,
      "updated": 1703342896
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f32faff09e0000b4bf78",
      "text": "　\t\t\t忘れるとXとのリンクが切れちゃう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342896,
      "updated": 1703342898
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf62",
      "text": "　　AIにやってほしいのはこれな感じがする[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342296
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf63",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703342105
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f019aff09e0000b4bf64",
      "text": "[「知識をひけらかすことは善である」という価値観]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342105,
      "updated": 1703781674
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f213aff09e0000d5c343",
      "text": "\t相手がついてこれるかどうかを気にせずに書きましょうということ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342612,
      "updated": 1703342643
    },
    {
      "id": "658721eaaff09e0000f0a36d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703354859,
      "updated": 1703383563
    },
    {
      "id": "658721eaaff09e0000f0a36e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703354859,
      "updated": 1703354859
    },
    {
      "id": "6586f20daff09e0000d5c342",
      "text": "[レクリエーションの会話]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1703342606,
      "updated": 1703354832
    },
    {
      "id": "658720b0aff09e0000f0a367",
